Class GridGraphManager.AnonymousGridGraphManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gridgraph.structure.GridGraphManager
      • com.gridgraph.structure.GridGraphManager.AnonymousGridGraphManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.server.GraphManager
    Enclosing class:
    GridGraphManager

    public static class GridGraphManager.AnonymousGridGraphManager
extends GridGraphManager
    Provides a unified way to construct a GridGraphManager for an application. With this instance, a GridGraphManager with default settings is constructs that could be used in the client side without needs to specifying details that're needed by a server application.
